Chi-X Warns Against ‘Too Big to Succeed’ Exchange, Boersen Says

-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 
2011-03-04T08:57:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-04/chi-x-warns-against-too-big-to-succeed-exchange-boersen-says.html
A giant exchange resulting from a
merger could be “too big to succeed,” according to Alasdair Haynes, chief executive officer of Chi-X Europe Ltd.,  Boersen-
Zeitun g reported, citing an interview with the CEO.  The CEO told the newspaper that there is a risk a giant
exchange could fail to implement technology changes quickly
enough because of its size.  To contact the reporter on this story:
